description:
Episode 2 - The Accidental Occidental Conception

When a Terra Cotta Warrior is brought back to life, The Middleman and Wendy set out to stop him before he can take the last living heir of the Qin dynasty to the land of the dead, releasing a hail of fire that will rain down on the Earth for a thousand years. With some help from fashionista and reformed succubus, Roxy Wasserman, the two must make a daring trip to the underworld to get the deed done. Still stinging from Wendy&#039;s harsh criticisms, Lacey lands herself a job as Roxy&#039;s assistant, which tests her activist spirit.
